The United States strongly condemns the recent terrorist attack on the Radisson Blu Hotel in Bamako, Mali. The attack has ended, and efforts are being made to locate all American citizens in Mali. Condolences are extended to the families of those killed and thoughts are with the injured. The bravery of the security personnel who responded to the situation is commended. The United States will continue to support the Government of Mali in their fight against terrorist groups and is ready to assist in the investigation of this attack.